*Glavna ulica* je bila puna ljudi. (The main street was full of people.)

*Glavni* grad je Beograd. (The capital city is Belgrade.)

*Glavnim* pravcem kretanja je bio istok. (The main direction of movement was east.)

*Glavno* je da svi zajedno napravimo dobru stvar. (The main thing is that we all do something good together.)

*Glavnim* problemom je bila nedostatak vode. (The main problem was the lack of water.)

*Glavna* tema rasprave je bila zdravlje. (The main topic of the discussion was health.)